      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POCKET POINT (4) has performed well at her last couple of runs here, most recently when third beaten one length (22.98). Form from her last run is proving strong. Rates highly and will give a great sight. STARLIGHT DUKE (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at this track following on from a second place finish (23.25) there the start prior. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Should be about the money. BRAVE CHOICE (8) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at this track over 400m behind Stop It Zipper (23.48) in a Grade 4/5. Was in the money the start prior. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Key runner on best form. GREAT NORTH (2) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
